Definition: showing skill and sensitivity in dealing with people
Example: by diplomatic conduct he avoided antagonizing anyone; a tactful way of correcting someone; the agency got the kid-glove treatment on Capitol Hill
Synonyms: noun, attribute, tactfulness, kid-glove, showing, skill, and, sensitivity, in, dealing, with, people, by, diplomatic, conduct, he, avoided, antagonizing, anyone, a, way, of, correcting, someone, the, agency, got, treatment, on, Capitol, Hill
Category: adj.all
